  "outcome": "A B2C notifier creates and submits a CHED-PP pre-notification end-to-end for an EU (France) origin consignment with two plant commodities (06011010, 06042090) entered manually, bulk-applied package/quantity details, transport by plane to a BCP, a phytosanitary certificate with file attachment, a newly created consignor reused as the consignee, and a declaration — receiving reference CHEDPP.GB.2026.1526069; a second browser context then acts as a BCP inspector, finds the CHED by reference in the decision service and records PHSI documentary, physical and identity checks as Compliant, ending on the CHED overview where the status label is asserted and the certificate is validated via two TRACES searchCertificate SOAP calls.",
  "notes": [
    "Two browser contexts on two hosts: notifier on https://importnotification-static-snd.azure.defra.cloud, inspector on https://importnotification-int-static-snd.azure.defra.cloud.",
